{"type": "article", "id": 10003, "title": "“Phree” 手写笔", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-26T07:24:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135614MQAEeqBXU0SdyFLm.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t以色列科技公司 OTM 推出了一款叫做 “Phree” 的手写笔，采用 3D 激光专利技术，跟踪使用者的手部动作和精确的笔画，可以在任何表面上书写，如手机，平板电脑，笔记本电脑，电视等，并且即时在手机上显示出来。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"http://otmtech.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061356104n3CwHt0ahorZKgu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135611tJ7vjfoh1sIO4QiB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135611wQb6cedSK45VI1mO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135611nVMh7Bwb2JUCvWmP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.13569682\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135612E1euG8fnC6DjIJQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135612Vpa86b7UHicNSOPq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56723716\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}